@page "/raids"

<div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-800 to-red-700 py-16">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Raid Boosting</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-white mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      Conquiste as raids mais desafiadoras e garanta os melhores equipamentos com nossa equipe de
      elite. Do Normal ao Mítico, nós te levamos ao topo.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Por que escolher nosso boost de raids?</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg
            class="h-6 w-6 text-purple-600 mr-2"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke="currentColor">
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span>Equipe composta por raiders de guilds de top mundial</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg
            class="h-6 w-6 text-purple-600 mr-2"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke="currentColor">
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span>Garantia de loot específico para seu personagem</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg
            class="h-6 w-6 text-purple-600 mr-2"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke="currentColor">
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span>Disponibilidade para todas as dificuldades: Normal, Heroico e Mítico</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg
            class="h-6 w-6 text-purple-600 mr-2"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke="currentColor">
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span>Conquistas e montarias raras garantidas</span>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div class="mt-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Raids disponíveis:</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li>• Aberrus, o Crisol Sombreado (Última temporada)</li>
          <li>• Cofre das Encarnações</li>
          <li>• Sepulcro dos Fundadores</li>
          <li>• Outras raids sob consulta</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 border border-gray-200">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">Escolha seu pacote</h3>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div
            class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-purple-500 cursor-pointer transition">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="font-bold">Full Run Normal</span>
              <span class="text-xl font-bold">R$ 89,90</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-purple-500 cursor-pointer transition bg-purple-50">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <div>
                <span class="font-bold">Full Run Heroico</span>
                <span class="bg-green-500 text-white text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full ml-2"
                  >Mais Popular</span
                >
              </div>
              <span class="text-xl font-bold">R$ 199,90</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-purple-500 cursor-pointer transition">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="font-bold">Boss Específico Mítico</span>
              <span class="text-xl font-bold">R$ 129,90</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-purple-500 cursor-pointer transition">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="font-bold">Full Run Mítico</span>
              <span class="text-xl font-bold">R$ 599,90</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8">
          <button
            class="w-full bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-4 rounded-lg transition duration-300 mb-4">
            Adicionar ao Carrinho
          </button>
          <button
            class="w-full bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-4 rounded-lg transition duration-300">
            Comprar Agora
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
